    <div class="hero-block__column">
      <h1 class="hero-block__title">Why is the marscss framework different?</h1>
      <p>Unlike other CSS frameworks it works through mixins and not with rules, which allows us to have access to an infinite number of possibilities without adding a line to CSS file</p>

      <p>Although there are mechanisms to generate css such as builders or components, their potential lies in that they in turn work generating code from mixins with what can be rewritten.</p>
