<div class="hero-block" data-onscreen id="home-install">
  <div class="hero-block__container">
    <div class="hero-block__column">
      <h1 class="hero-block__title">
        How to use?
      </h1>

      <h2 class="h3">Install the dependency</h2>

      <% markdown do %>
      ~~~shell
      npm i @marsbased/marscss --save
      ~~~~
      <% end %>

      <h2 class="h3">Use it from your main scss file:</h2>

      <% markdown do %>
      ~~~scss
      @import 'node_modules/@marsbased/marscss';
      ~~~
      <% end %>

      <p>
      Alternatively, if you are using a bundler you probably can use a shortcut like:
      </p>

      <% markdown do %>
      ~~~scss
      @import '~@marsbased/marscss';
      ~~~
      <% end %>
